          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乐善的必生余庆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黑虎玄坛坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸾鹤纷纷下九天，财源滚滚庆丰年。享受千载皇家禄，皆是阴功绩德全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃龙虎玄坛是也。手执金轮如意，默起千祥吉庆。跨着黑虎，行着大有之年，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "所到之处，无不雨顺风调，国泰民安。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五谷丰登天下乐，民安物阜贺升平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四云童、五天官同上，同挖门，同归坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "民安物阜风光好，五谷丰登兆。舜日与尧天，圣德齐天乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祝遐龄爵位高，祝丰年长生不老。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾等乃天官是也。今有下界福主，阴功浩大，积德累功。奉上帝敕旨，命吾招"
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "聚财源，献与福地。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "积善人家当德报，存心自有上苍知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命招集财源，俱已聚齐，请天官赐福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速诏五路财神来者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领钧旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黑虎玄坛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招财、利市。"
        },
        {
          "character": "招财、利市",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
