          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "速请五路财神来者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "招财、利市",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（招财、利市同同。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五天官 （同石榴花） 只见那香风阵阵献氤氲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "簇簇的子气满阶庭。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勤读的加官进爵，宠锡君恩。"
