          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天官相诏，一同进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "时运、金神、银神、催财",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "时运、金神、银神、催财",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天官在上，我等参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五路天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将一应财源，献与福主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "催旺、时运",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（催旺、时运同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "五路天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等先赠其财，后赐其福，真乃财源辐辏也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同斗鹌鹑） 这的是广众福田临，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日个添来福份尽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐献那财源茂盛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玳筵前满泛着——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同夹白） 哎——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同斗鹌鹑） 金樽，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要与那福主称庆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（催旺、时运引四回回招聚宝盒同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "催旺、时运",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一群财源献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五路天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙啊！缕缕银光透，层层金气浮。好一座金穴银山也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同上小楼） 只见那金银，灿灿灿光明，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜的是金穴银山，库满箱盈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龟鹤宏源，陶朱堪趁，一任价东西行运。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。五路天官同下高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "五路天官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幅辏已全，一同回奏上帝者。请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同煞尾） 听悠扬一派洞仙音，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐齐的跨鹤乘鸾上码云。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "指日里称庆丰年定太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众车同斜门拥众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
